import axios from 'axios' import React, { useState } from 'react' const Login = () => { const [login, setLogin] = useState({}) const handlerLog=(e)=>{ e.preventDefault() axios.post("/api/log", login) .then(()=>{ console.log() }) } return ( <>
setLogin({...login, email: e.target.value})} value={login.email}/>
We'll never share your email with anyone else.
setLogin({...login, password: e.target.value})} value={login.password}/>
) } export default Login
